ebf6d26 - New method InitPar([type] initial_value,"name ?? # comments") is added. This method give return initial_value if parameter do not exist. Return existing value if exist. As a long term goal, this this will replace Require and GetPar methods. - int n parameter is added to GetV*(int n) methods. n=0: all, n>0: upto n-elements, n<0: remove n elements from the back. - Options in GetLine and Print methods are changed.
cbf9fd3 - configuration lilak config_test command added. This will create and test all lilak configuration files without running cmake or make. - geant4/nptool lilak compilation with nptool is stablized using nptool directories under lilak/source projects. Users need to create class inheriting G4VUserDetectorConstruction (DetectorConstruction) under geant4 (nptool) directory and run simulation using lilak g4sim (nptool). Feature work todo: all nessesary parameters will be collected and printed out if no input configuration is given. LKNPToolRunManager inheriting LKG4RunManager runs nptool simulation using nptool libraries. LKG4DetectorConstructionFactory and LKNPDetectorConstructionFactory: will be created from lilak_configuration, which are detector construction collection from geant4 and geant4+nptool. Factory classes are use from the run managers. LKG4DetectorConstruction, LKNPDetectorConstruction: default detector construction with empty world  are added for test run.
